```class Solution {
    public double minTime(int n, int k, int m, int[] time, double[] mul) {
        double res = 0;
        int stage = 0;
        int left = n;
        Arrays.sort(time);
        while (left > 0) {
            int depart = Math.min(left, k);
            double departTime = time[time.length - depart] * mul[stage];
            res += departTime;
            left -= depart;
            stage = (stage + 1 + (int) Math.floor(departTime)) % m;
            if (left > 0) {
                res += time[time.length - left] * mul[stage];
                left = 0;
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
